#  Name:
#     ncar_link

#  Purpose:
#     Generate linker (ld) arguments for linking NCAR library.

#  Language:
#     Bourne Shell

#  Type of Module:
#     Shell script.

#  Description:
#     This script should be invoked when linking against the NCAR library.
#     Use the -star option when linking with SNX.

